                  </hi>. I work for my father, who is a gardener. on the 25th of December I came to Porchester-terrace, and saw Wale and the</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183801010055"></xptr>
               <p>prisoner struggling—I saw the other man go up with a sledge-hammer, and swear he would kill him—I am sure the prisoner is the person.</p>
